| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0400 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a967cac8-5ebc-5ceb-8b4a-b4c305de24f1"
